<td class="mbox-text" style="">This article <b>is incomplete, and may require expansion or <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Cleanup" title="Wikipedia:Cleanup">cleanup</a></b>. Please help to improve the article, or discuss the issue on the <a href="/wiki/Talk:Theory_of_cognitive_development" title="Talk:Theory of cognitive development">talk page</a>.</td>
